title: Sidewall, ca. 1930
creditline: Gift of Mark Bitter, Robert Bitter, Ward Bitter, and Tami Bitter Cook
description: Cubist-inspired design. Very geometric with cubes of simulated marble and floral motifs. Printed on background of simulated marble. Printed on ungrounded paper.
